  <brief_title>Therapeutic Hypothermia for Severe Traumatic Brain Injury in Japan</brief_title>
  <official_title>Therapeutic Strategy for Severe Head Trauma Patients With Mild Hypothermia and Estimation of Medical Expenses in Japan</official_title>
